in_seq = [(value, 10) for value in range(0, 7 + 1)]
out_seq = [0, 1, {2, 3}]
tim_seq = [10, 15, 15]
async with subscription_streamer(in_seq) as subs:

    async def the_stream():
        s = subs.subscribe(15, None, None)
        for i in range(3):
            yield await s.__anext__()
        await s.aclose()
    with assertPassed(sum(tim_seq)):
        await assert_stream(tim_seq, out_seq, the_stream())
pytest.mark.trio
